Changelog
=========
0.7 (March 2020)
----------------
* patch up for py 3 and dj 1.11

0.6 (unreleased)
----------------

* Nothing changed yet.

0.5 (2013-07-26)
----------------

* Updated to django-mail-factory 0.7.


0.4 (2013-05-13)
----------------

* Remove deprecated, use hashlib
* Update translations


0.3 (2013-04-03)
----------------

* French translation
* django-mail-factory integration
* Registration email validation supports
* Add resend and cancel email request error
* Add Changelog and Version
* Fixes novagile/postbox#546 - email_verify shouldn't use login_required
* Add mail_factory + email request on user creation
* PEP-8 + settings.SUPPORT_EMAIL
* Make django-email-change compliant with settings.SITE_NAME and settings.SITE_URL
* Use templateview instead of direct_to_template
* Fix setup.py
* Fix manifest
* README in RestructuredText


0.2.2 (2011-02-23)
----------------

* Forked version from https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-email-change